OL,7,FShropshire Council disputed the
OL,8,Fclaims, arguing planning permission to
OL,9,Fbuild the farm was granted following
OL,10,Fdiscussion with the Environment
OL,11,FAgency, Natural England, and the
OL,12,Fcouncil's ecology and public
OL,13,Fprotection teams.
OL,15,FOn Tuesday (17 June), the High Court
OL,16,Fruled that the Council "failed to
OL,17,Fcarry out a legally adequate
OL,18,Fassessment of the effect of the
OL,19,Fspreading of digestate on third party
OL,20,Fland."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
