OL,5,Cfears
OL,7,FThe judge added: "The Council failed
OL,8,Fto carry out a lawful appropriate
OL,9,Fassessment before granting the
OL,10,Fpermission, failing to carry out a
OL,11,Flawful in-combination assessment of
OL,12,Fthe development's impacts."
OL,14,F"Putting our rivers at risk"
OL,16,FFollowing the ruling, Dr Alison
OL,17,FCaffyn, River Action's advisory board
OL,18,Fmember and local campaigner, said:
OL,19,F"There are nearly 65 chickens for
OL,20,Fevery person in Shropshire and yet the
OL,21,Fcouncil still thought we needed more.
