OL,7,F"This ruling proves what we've said
OL,8,Fall along: the planning system has
OL,9,Fbeen putting our rivers at risk.
OL,11,F"This case is a win for communities
OL,12,Facross the UK who are standing up to
OL,13,Fthe environmental degradation caused
OL,14,Fby industrial factory farming."
OL,16,FThis hearing follows last month's
OL,17,Flandmark judgment in National Farmers
OL,18,FUnion v Herefordshire County Council,
OL,19,Fwhere the High Court declared farming
OL,20,Fmanure as waste.
